Surgeries_Universities_in_Canada\" title=\"Top Surgeries Universities in Canada\">Top Surgeries Universities in Canada<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>Becoming a Thoracic Surgeon is easy when you follow the right path and the right foundation after reading this text you will e enlighten on how to achieve your dream goal learn more below:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2291 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/new-image-thorcic-surgeon-Canada-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"How to become a Thoracic Surgeon\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83049715\">Definition<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83049716\">Duties They Carried out<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83049717\">Conditions Thoracic Surgeon Treat<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83049718\">Education and Training<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83049719\">Subjects requirements<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83049720\">Thoracic Surgeon Salary<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc83049721\">Top Surgeries Universities in Canada<\/a><\/p>\n<h3 id=\"definition\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Definition\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83049715\"><\/a>Definition<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2292 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/thoracic-surgery-fellow-mn-hero-3597103_0002-512x512px-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" title=\"\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>A specialized thoracic surgeon treats lung and esophageal cancer, while specialized surgeons treat the heart.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"duties-they-carried-out\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Duties_They_Carried_out\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83049716\"><\/a>Duties They Carried out<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>These set of surgeons specializes in dealing with disease or injuries to the structures inside your chest, and the following:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Pericardium (the membrane around the heart)<\/li>\n<li>Trachea (windpipe)<\/li>\n<li>Esophagus (the tube leading to the stomach)<\/li>\n<li>Lungs<\/li>\n<li>Pleura (membranes around the lungs)<\/li>\n<li>Mediastinum (the area that separates the lungs and holds the heart)<\/li>\n<li>Diaphragm<\/li>\n<li>Chest wall<\/li>\n<li>Coronary arteries<u>,<\/u> valves, and myocardium<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2290 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/labeled-heart-300x221.jpg\" alt=\"How to become a Thoracic Surgeon\" width=\"300\" height=\"221\" title=\"\"><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"conditions-thoracic-surgeon-treat\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Conditions_Thoracic_Surgeon_Treat\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83049717\"><\/a>Conditions Thoracic Surgeon Treat<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><strong><em>They treat variety of disorders such as:<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Chest reconstruction<\/li>\n<li>Heart transplants<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-2288 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/images-5.jpg\" alt=\"How to become a Thoracic Surgeon\" width=\"259\" height=\"195\" title=\"\"><\/li>\n<li>Lung cancer<\/li>\n<li>Heart lesions including coronary artery disease and valve disorders<\/li>\n<li>Benign (noncancerous)<\/li>\n<li>Esophagus cancer<\/li>\n<li>Gastroesophageal reflux disease<\/li>\n<li>Lung transplant<\/li>\n<li>Emphysema<\/li>\n<li>Mesothelioma<\/li>\n<li>Tracheal resection.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Thoracic surgeons mainly treat lung cancer, lung disease, and disease in the esophagus and chest wall. Cardiothoracic surgeons, by contrast, operate on more disease in organs in the chest and in the chest cavity.<\/p>\n<p>Thoracic surgeons mainly treat lung cancer, lung disease, and diseases in the esophagus and chest wall. Cardiothoracic surgeons, by contrast, operate on more diseases in organs in the chest and in the chest cavity.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"education-and-training-how-to-become-a-thoracic-surgeon\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Education_and_Training_How_to_become_a_Thoracic_Surgeon\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83049718\"><\/a>Education and Training| How to become a Thoracic Surgeon<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>A thoracic surgery certification requires years of education and training, including:<\/li>\n<li>A 4-year undergraduate degree, often in pre-med<\/li>\n<li>A medical degree<\/li>\n<li>A 5-year general surgery residency<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"subjects-requirements-how-to-become-a-thoracic-surgeon\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Subjects_requirements_How_to_become_a_Thoracic_Surgeon\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83049719\"><\/a>Subjects requirements| How to become a Thoracic Surgeon<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>All students interested in becoming a surgeon are required to take the following subjects outline below:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Mathematics<\/li>\n<li>English<\/li>\n<li>Biology<\/li>\n<li>Chemistry<\/li>\n<li>Physics and calculus<\/li>\n<li>As well advice to sign up for psychology to learn more about the human nature and explore the mind-body connection.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 id=\"estimated-salary\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Estimated_Salary\"><\/span>Estimated Salary<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"114\"><\/td>\n<td width=\"90\"><strong><em>Annual Salary<\/em><\/strong><\/td>\n<td width=\"108\"><strong><em>Weekly Pay<\/em><\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"114\">Top Earners<\/td>\n<td width=\"90\">$400,000<\/td>\n<td width=\"108\">$7,692<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"114\">75th Percentile<\/td>\n<td width=\"90\">$400,000<\/td>\n<td width=\"108\">$7,692<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"114\">Average<\/td>\n<td width=\"90\">$290,486<\/td>\n<td width=\"108\">$5,586<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"114\">25th Percentile<\/td>\n<td width=\"90\">$126,500<\/td>\n<td width=\"108\">$2,432<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h3 id=\"top-surgeries-universities-in-canada\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Top_Surgeries_Universities_in_Canada\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc83049721\"><\/a>Top Surgeries Universities in Canada<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>University of Manitoba<\/li>\n<li>University of Ottawa<\/li>\n<li>University of Montreal<\/li>\n<li>The University of Alberta<\/li>\n<li>University of Calgary<\/li>\n<li>McMaster University<\/li>\n<li>University of Calgary<\/li>\n<li>Western University<\/li>\n<li>University of Toronto<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-2293 alignright\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Toronto-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" title=\"\"><\/li>\n<li>McGill University<\/li>\n<li>University of the British Columbia.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em><strong>See also &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<\/strong><\/em><\/span><a title=\"How to become Orthopedic Surgeon\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-become-orthopedic-surgeon\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em><strong>How to become Orthopedic Surgeon<\/strong><\/em><\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"How to become a Thoracic Surgeon \u2013Definition, Conditions they treat, Duties thoracic surgeon carries out, Subjects Requirements, Top&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2289,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[729],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"